<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF108-114-768  </DOCNO><DOCID>08 114 768.andO;</DOCID><JOURNAL>Classroom Computer Learning  Jan 1990 v10 n4 p42(6).andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>Macintosh-like word processors for your Apple II. (SoftwareReview) (educational software)(includes related article ontesting) (evaluation)</TITLE><AUTHOR>Eiser, Leslie.andM;</AUTHOR><TEXT><ABSTRACT>Since MacWrite's word processor came on the market other vendorshave introduced Macintosh-like word processor programs for AppleII.andP;  American School Publishers' IIWrite 2.01, at $49.95, hasimitated the look and feel of MacWrite the best of all theprograms reviewed.andP;  The interface looks very similar, the fontslook good on screen, and the pull-down menus, error messages andother recognizable features will make the user feel at home.andO;However, the amount of text it can handle is limited, and the200-word capacity of the clipboard is also restrictive.andO;Scholastic Inc's MultiScribe 3.01c, at $99.95, has only a slightresemblance to MacWrite, and has gone through many revisions,resulting in increased speed, power, and flexibility.andP;  Drawbacksinclude lack of Undo and Online Help features.andP;  BerkeleySoftworks' GeoWrite 3.3, at $69.95, is part of a larger softwarepackage called GEOS.andP;  GeoWrite has many features of a desktoppublishing package.andP;  Printing is easy and quick, even withgraphics.andP;  Pages are handled independently, and can be captured asa unit.andP;  The product has an excellent selection of fonts.andO;However, on-screen performance is very slow.andP;  Roger WagnerPublishing Inc's MouseWrite, at $149.95, has the most interestingcompromise between features and speed.andP;  MouseWrite quicklycompletes actions that other products are slow to finish.andO;However, MouseWrite gave up quality screen design to achieve thatspeed.andP;  A comprehensive chart covering evaluation results for allproducts reviewed is included.andM;</ABSTRACT></TEXT><DESCRIPT>Company:   American School Publishers (products)Scholastic Inc. (products)Berkeley Softworks (products)Roger Wagner Publishing Inc. (products)Apple Computer Inc. (products).andO;Ticker:    AAPL.andO;Product:   MacWrite (Word processing software) (usage)IIWrite 2.01 (Educational software)MultiScribe 3.01c (Educational software)GeoWrite 3.3 (Educational software)MouseWrite 2.6.8B (Educational software).andO;Topic:     Educational SoftwareWord Processing SoftwareEvaluation.andO;Feature:   illustrationtable.andO;Caption:   Macintosh-like word processors. (table)andM;</DESCRIPT></DOC>